==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Pur
<hw>Pur</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The low, murmuring sound made by a cat
to express contentment or pleasure.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>purr</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Purana</ent>⟦br⟧
